The paper deals with medical image analysis using convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques to optimize the imputation and segmentation networks, which falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper involves the synthesis of images, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM).
